OL,3,CEamonn Holmes 'doing okay' following
OL,4,Cstroke, says son
OL,6,FTV presenter Eamonn Holmes is "doing
OL,7,Fokay given the circumstances" after he
OL,8,Fsuffered a stroke, his eldest son
OL,9,FDeclan has said.
OL,11,FDeclan Holmes added his father's
OL,12,Fmedical issue "came as a real shock",
OL,13,Fand he thanked those who have sent
OL,14,Fmessages of support, saying: "It means
OL,15,Fa lot to us as a family."
OL,17,FGB News announced on Saturday that
OL,18,FHolmes, 66, had suffered a stroke last
OL,19,Fweek and was recovering in hospital.
OL,26,@nD@_OUoD@]O]tD@OOUtD@dO]vD@^OUwD@YO]
