OL,3,CEamonn Holmes 'doing okay' following
OL,4,Cstroke, says son
OL,6,FIn a statement on Sunday, his son
OL,7,Fsaid: "What happened came as a real
OL,8,Fshock, but dad is doing okay given the
OL,9,Fcircumstances and we're taking it one
OL,10,Fstep at a time.
OL,12,F"I just wanted to share a quick
OL,13,Fmessage to say we hugely appreciate
OL,14,Fall the messages, it means a lot to us
OL,15,Fas a family.
OL,17,F"For now, we're focused on him and
OL,18,Fkeeping things steady around him.
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776096667
OL,3,CEamonn Holmes 'doing okay' following
OL,4,Cstroke, says son
OL,6,F"We'd really value a bit of privacy as
OL,7,Fwe navigate it, and what lies ahead,
OL,8,Fbut thank-you again for the support as
OL,9,Fit means so much to dad and the rest
OL,10,Fof the family."
OL,12,FIn a statement on Saturday, a GB News
OL,13,Fspokesperson said Holmes "was taken
OL,14,Fill last week and it was later
OL,15,Fconfirmed he had suffered a stroke".
OL,17,FThe statement added: "He is currently
OL,18,Fresponding well to treatment.
OL,20,F"Eamonn has asked for privacy as he
OL,21,Ffocuses on getting better.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@OO]uD@ZOUwD@cO]yD@VOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
