OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776096667
OL,3,CEamonn Holmes 'doing okay' following
OL,4,Cstroke, says son
OL,6,F"His colleagues and everyone at GB
OL,7,FNews wish him a speedy recovery and
OL,8,Flook forward to welcoming him back to
OL,9,Fthe people's channel when he is ready
OL,10,Fto return."
OL,12,FAlex Armstrong will present in his
OL,13,Fabsence this week, the broadcaster
OL,14,Fadded.
OL,16,FHolmes, from Northern Ireland, who
OL,17,Fpresents GB News Breakfast with his co-
OL,18,Fhost Ellie Costello, is Britain's
OL,19,Flongest-serving breakfast news
OL,20,Fpresenter, with a career spanning more
OL,21,Fthan 40 years.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]
