OL,3,CEamonn Holmes 'doing okay' following
OL,4,Cstroke, says son
OL,6,FBefore joining GB News in 2022, he
OL,7,Fanchored GMTV between 1993 and 2005,
OL,8,FSky News Sunrise between 2005 and
OL,9,F2016, and co-presented ITV's This
OL,10,FMorning from 2006 to 2021.
OL,12,FAngelos Frangopoulos, chief executive
OL,13,Fof GB News, said on Saturday: "Eamonn
OL,14,Fis a loved member of the GB News
OL,15,Ffamily, and we're with him every step
OL,16,Fof the way as he recovers."
OL,26,@uD@_OUxD@[O]
