OL,3,CEamonn Holmes 'doing okay' following
OL,4,Cstroke, says son
OL,6,FHolmes has long battled health issues
OL,7,Fafter dislodging discs in his back
OL,8,Fwhich he said previously impinged on
OL,9,Fhis sciatic nerve and affected the
OL,10,Fmobility of his right leg.
OL,12,FHe previously spoke about going
OL,13,Fthrough spinal surgery, a double hip
OL,14,Freplacement, and his struggles walking
OL,15,Fand using a mobility scooter.
OL,17,FHolmes had two falls in May last year
OL,18,Fwhich seem to have taken place only
OL,19,Fweeks apart.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
