OL,3,CEamonn Holmes 'doing okay' following
OL,4,Cstroke, says son
OL,6,FThe former This Morning host was taken
OL,7,Fto hospital after a first fall at his
OL,8,Fhome, then fell from his chair live on-
OL,9,Fair.
